{
  "texts": [
    "We then asked for the treatment plan.",
    "Question 2: \"What is your treatment plan for your most likely diagnosis?",
    "Please include any consults, laboratory or radiographic studies, and treatments (medical and/or surgical) in your response.\"",
    "Subsequently, attending doctors were invited to assess the complexity of the clinical scenarios and their alignment with ChatGPT's responses regarding differential diagnoses and treatment plans, using a fivepoint Likert scale.",
    "The difficulty scale was (1) very simple, (2) simple, (3) neutral, (4) difficult, and (5) very difficult."
  ]
}